    {\displaystyle \left|\psi (0)\right\rangle }
   is let to evolve for an interval 
  
    
      
        δ
        t
      
    
    {\displaystyle \delta t}
   by the Schrödinger equation it becomes

  
    
      
        
          |
          
            ψ
            (
            δ
            t
            )
          
          ⟩
        
        =
        
          ∑
          
            n
          
        
        
